# Binary Search Tree

```python
class BST:

    def insert(
    self,
    root,
    val
    ):

        if root is None:
            return TreeNode(val)

        if val<root.val:
            root.left=self.insert(
            root.left,
            val
            )

        else:
            root.right=self.insert(
            root.right,
            val
            )

        return root
```

